companyName: O'Shares FTSE Russell Small Cap Quality Dividend
description:
The investment seeks to track the performance (before fees and expenses) of the FTSE USA Small Cap ex Real Estate 2Qual/Vol/Yield 3% Capped Factor Index.
 Under normal market conditions, the fund will invest at least 80% of its total assets in the components of the index. The index is constructed using a proprietary, rules-based methodology designed to select equity securities from the FTSE USA Small Cap Index that have exposure to the following three factors: 1) quality, 2) low volatility and 3) yield.
